data.description:
Beautiful open-concept ranch home with three bedrooms and a home-office that can be converted to a fourth bedroom. Master suite has a large walk-in closet, dual sinks, garden tub & separate shower. A spacious island kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite counters.Wood like Tile flooring 9-feet high ceilings, recessed lights, and a good size backyard with a covered patio. A great community with pools, sport fields, parks, and stocked ponds. Ready to move in. Must see.

The tenant has pay all utilities. The income has to be three times more than a rent
